message.body: Should I be totally stoked about riding bikes???
Yes!!! I'll wear so many layers it will be hard to pedal!
What time shall we head out!
We should get there at 1:30. What do u think? And where do I meet u?
Yeah let's meet at 1:15. Wanna take powelton? We can meet at walnut and 49th or 48th. I forget which is closer to you.
Ok. 1:15 at 48. (I've been gnawing thru this brownie since 7:30. Yum.)
Hahaha. Sounds gooooood. Okay see ya there!
